OL,3,CDavid and Victoria Beckham wish son
OL,4,CBrooklyn happy birthday amid family
OL,5,Cfeud
OL,7,FIn January, following months of
OL,8,Frumours, Brooklyn launched a lengthy
OL,9,Fattack on both his parents in an
OL,10,FInstagram post, accusing them of
OL,11,Fcontrolling behaviour, putting "brand
OL,12,FBeckham" before all else, and trying
OL,13,Fto "endlessly ruin" his relationship
OL,14,Fwith wife Nicola Peltz Beckham on
OL,15,Fseveral occasions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772701496
OL,3,CDavid and Victoria Beckham wish son
OL,4,CBrooklyn happy birthday amid family
OL,5,Cfeud
OL,7,FSpecifically, he addressed the
OL,8,Fallegation that Peltz had refused to
OL,9,Fwear a wedding dress designed by
OL,10,FVictoria, with Brooklyn claiming it
OL,11,Fwas Victoria who pulled out of the
OL,12,Farrangement at the last minute,
OL,13,Fforcing Peltz to find something else
OL,14,Fto wear.
OL,16,FBrooklyn accused his mother of dancing
OL,17,F"very inappropriately" with him at his
OL,18,Fwedding, adding that he had "never
OL,19,Ffelt more uncomfortable or humiliated
OL,20,Fin my entire life".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772701496
OL,3,CDavid and Victoria Beckham wish son
OL,4,CBrooklyn happy birthday amid family
OL,5,Cfeud
OL,7,FHowever, this has been disputed by
OL,8,Fsome guests. DJ Fat Tony told ITV that
OL,9,Fthe dance was "awkward", but the
OL,10,Fbiggest upset came from Marc Anthony
OL,11,Fcalling Victoria Beckham the most
OL,12,Fbeautiful woman in the room instead of
OL,13,Fthe bride.
OL,15,FMarc Anthony has said the way the feud
OL,16,Fhas played out is "hardly the truth".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
